ELM369 Priority Software License (concept model)

5. Ownership
All intellectual property rights remain with the creator.

4. Priority Modules
Core engines, algorithms, and priority systems remain
restricted and may not be redistributed without permission.

3. Commercial Use
Commercial distribution or integration requires a royalty
agreement with the original author.

2. Attribution
Users must credit the original creator and project name.

1. Grant of Use
The software may be used freely for personal, educational,
and non-commercial purposes.